OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776953471
OL,3,CSerial sex predator caught after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough 28 years on
OL,6,FA serial sex predator who attacked a
OL,7,Fwoman in her home 28 years ago was
OL,8,Fcaught after police matched his DNA to
OL,9,Fother sexually motivated burglaries.
OL,11,FAndrew Pennington jumped out on the
OL,12,Fwoman as she arrived home from work at
OL,13,Fthe house in Beverley, East Yorkshire,
OL,14,Fin the early hours of 23 July, 1998.
OL,16,FHe tried to remove her clothes and
OL,17,Fthreatened to rape and beat her,
OL,18,Fbefore he was disturbed and chased
OL,19,Ffrom the scene by a lodger.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
