PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776953471
OL,3,CSerial sex predator caught after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough 28 years on
OL,6,FLimited forensic developments meant
OL,7,Fthe investigation stalled at the time.
OL,9,FBut detectives re-examining the case
OL,10,Fin September 2025 linked samples from
OL,11,Fthe victim's clothes to Pennington,
OL,12,Fwhose DNA had been taken in relation
OL,13,Fto a previous offence.
OL,15,FHe had been jailed in 2017 for raping
OL,16,Fa woman in North Yorkshire in 1988 as
OL,17,Fwell as three burglaries in 1997, the
OL,18,Flatter of which all had his DNA taken
OL,19,Ffrom the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
