PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776953471
OL,3,CSerial sex predator caught after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough 28 years on
OL,6,FDetectives interviewed Pennington last
OL,7,Fmonth, during which he admitted the
OL,8,FBeverley attack, as well as a separate
OL,9,Fburglary from 1997 in which he
OL,10,Fconfessed to stealing underwear, cash
OL,11,Fand photographs .
OL,13,FThe 62-year-old, from Rawcliffe, East
OL,14,FYorkshire, pleaded guilty at Hull
OL,15,FCrown Court to attempted rape,
OL,16,Findecent assault, burglary and
OL,17,Fburglary with intent to steal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
