PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776953471
OL,3,CSerial sex predator caught after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough 28 years on
OL,6,FDet Con Eleanor Henrickson, of
OL,7,FHumberside Police, described
OL,8,FPennington as a "sexual predator" who
OL,9,Fthought only of "his own sick desires"
OL,10,Fwhen breaking into the woman's home.
OL,12,F"Whilst prosecution was originally not
OL,13,Fan option due to a lack of evidence, I
OL,14,Fam pleased that justice will now be
OL,15,Fserved," she said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
