PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1776953471
OL,3,CSerial sex predator caught after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough 28 years on
OL,6,F"I hope this case sends a stark
OL,7,Fmessage to anyone that has ever
OL,8,Fcommitted an offence and thinks they
OL,9,Fhave got away with it. We will keep
OL,10,Fsearching and we will do everything in
OL,11,Four power to hold you accountable for
OL,12,Fyour crimes.
OL,14,F"Nobody should be made to feel unsafe
OL,15,Fin their own home and I want to praise
OL,16,Fthe victim for her courage in coming
OL,17,Fforward and her patience over the
OL,18,Fyears."
OL,20,FPennington will be sentenced next
OL,21,Fmonth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@GO]
